Constantino et al., 2010
). Ecuador :Provinces of Zamora and Pichincha (GBIF,2020). Peru : Departments of Lambayeque and Loreto (Iquitos) (GBIF, 2020). Venezuela : States of Anzoátegui (San Tome), Aragua , Caracas (Campo Alegre), Mérida , Miranda (El Hatillo), Monagas , Sucre , and Táchira , ( Fernández de Varela, 1982 ;
Thomé et al., 1997
; GBIF, 2020).
